OL,3,CFire on Little Sark thought to have
OL,4,Cbeen started by discarded glass bottles
OL,6,FThe gorse wildfire swept across Little
OL,7,FSark on Friday 10 July and led to five
OL,8,Ffirefighter being injured.
OL,10,FDuring its height, the blaze is
OL,11,Fbelieved to have covered around 20,000
OL,12,Fsquare meters of scrubland.
OL,14,FThe Chief Fire Officer said: "The heat
OL,15,Fwas so intense, that even the
OL,16,Fofficers' boots started to melt."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
